{"tid":43723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12月20-23日 香港會有個『劫』","createTime":"2016-12-17T16:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T08:42:17.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a13a6b3171135a4f3888e0da9d9174aba066d65","tid":43723,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">12月20-23日 香港會有個『劫』??</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日收到朋友一個未能百分百確定既消息，<br />\n朋友話佢媽咪信佛教，早幾日有個師傅同佢講，<br />\n話算到香港下星期 (12月20-23日) 會有個『劫』，<br />\n叫佢通知其他人，帶定兩支水、兩排朱古力同一件衫出街，冇咩事亦唔好出街，<br />\n如萬一有任何事發生，都千奇唔好人走你又走，冷靜搵一個較安全既地方，<br />\n唸住「南無阿彌陀佛」，如識唸佛經就唸佛經，<br />\n但如果過到呢個星期就應該冇咩事。<br />\n同埋呢位師傅舊年亦算過今年中國會有個『劫』，已經應咗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋友仲話佢媽咪睇過通勝，通勝都有講過今年香港有個『劫』，<br />\n另外亦記得有人幾年前已經同佢講過話香港喺 2016 年會有個『劫』！！<br />\n<br />\nPS&nbsp;: 以上內容純粹聽朋友既好心忠告，信不信由你，請勿誤會我喺度作估仔嚇大家！"},{"pid":"ff83311d71ecd6fd261fd8d604f86f2ad778771f","tid":43723,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314a6a9c12bb939d822998f792f5b7fab97b396e","tid":43723,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"c7f359dd71c21b2dbfd3ae2d7fd595493a82e891","tid":43723,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"奧運4年一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d5058196cd2531c8ae25d261f0e2c5b0803e83","tid":43723,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/005549_13d33a3ce2b07417cd8cd196dd64486a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.